=Sacrifice for Love=

10
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,980
=Episode 10=

11
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:50,860
(Are You in Love with My Dad?)

12
00:00:57,670 --> 00:00:59,560
Concubine Su, please help me
write the invitations.

13
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:01,280
The betrothal party is coming.

14
00:01:04,710 --> 00:01:05,430
Why are you here?

15
00:01:06,430 --> 00:01:08,400
I asked Concubine Su to help me
write the invitations

16
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:10,790
You won't refuse me, will you?

17
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,200
No, I won't.

18
00:01:18,350 --> 00:01:19,120
I'll write it.

19
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:24,150
All right. Nian, sit here.

20
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:26,510
It will be more comfortable.

21
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,000
Thank you.

22
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:38,760
Please teach me, darling.

23
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:46,230
Look, this is the HSBC…

24
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:52,400
No, thanks. Don't bother.

25
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,780
It's no bother.

26
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:59,760
You need to handle
the Chamber of Commerce.

27
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:03,920
Nian will help write them.
And I'll keep her company.

28
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:07,510
Yeah. We haven't chosen our dresses yet.

29
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,000
Yichuan,

30
00:02:09,430 --> 00:02:11,590
let's take some time
to choose our dresses.

31
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,220
(Invitation)
I'm busy with the Chamber of Commerce.

32
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:17,470
Let's check the dresses later.

33
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,600
The invitations have all been sent out.

34
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:29,750
This is the guest list.
Please take a look.

35
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:35,000
They are all honored guests.
Take good care of them.

36
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:38,910
This way.

37
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,140
- Hello, Mr. Lu, Concubine Su.
- Master.

38
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,590
Young master, Miss Lu.

39
00:02:45,870 --> 00:02:47,710
Yichuan has been busy recently.

40
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:49,750
- So I had the tailor come over.
- That's fine.

41
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:51,910
To take your measurements
and alter the dress.

42
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,900
Could you please get up,
Mr. Lu Yichuan?

43
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,590
It won't take you too long.

44
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,080
Please take off your jacket.

45
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,190
I'll do the rest.

46
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:30,680
Give me that.

47
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:51,840
It's your job.

48
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:52,520
Okay.

49
00:03:57,400 --> 00:04:00,710
Nian, you should
buy some new clothes too.

50
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:01,750
Let her take your measurements.

51
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,750
My clothes were made by the same store.

52
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:09,380
She must have kept my measurements.

53
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:11,000
There's no need to measure again.

54
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,710
Yes. We have kept
all the measurements.

55
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:17,480
Concubine Su, our store has got
some Lingyun silk.

56
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:18,780
It is the only one in Nancheng.

57
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:20,240
I've brought it here for you,

58
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,800
hoping you can like it.

59
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,120
Nian, take a look at it.

60
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,040
Look, how soft it is!

61
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,310
Keep it if you like it.

62
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:44,510
No problem, Mr. Lu.

63
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,000
Take her to settle the bill.

64
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,190
Yes, Master.

65
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,980
The only Lingyun silk in Nancheng.

66
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,240
And you decided to
give it to her, not me.

67
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:05,000
Dad, you are so biased.

68
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:06,870
Xiaoqian!

69
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,560
What do you mean?

70
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,480
What do you mean?

71
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,800
You let her touch you!

72
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,270
She took your measurements personally.
You must be so happy.

73
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,480
Are you in love with her?

74
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:35,720
What about you?
The only Lingyun silk in Nancheng

75
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,510
is given to you. Are you happy?

76
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,190
Are you in love with my dad?

77
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:43,310
It's none of your business.

78
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:49,240
Fine. Then stay away from my business.

79
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,240
Chun.

80
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,830
Put this in the soup for Su Kenian.

81
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,000
What's this?

82
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,310
Just do as I say.

83
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,630
Who the hell is Su Kenian?

84
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:22,120
How dare she seduce Master
in front of me?

85
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:30,480
I just can't let it go
if I don't teach her a lesson.

86
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,920
Let's eat.

87
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:37,750
Xiaoqian went to see her grandma.
No need to wait for her.

88
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,430
Here is your soup.

89
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:50,800
Put the bowl here.

90
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:04,070
Concubine Zhang, thank you
for handling the family affairs.

91
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,270
Indeed. Take the soup.

92
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:37,240
Chun, how dare you
poison Concubine Su!

93
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,720
Someone! Get her out
and beat her to death!

94
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:43,630
I didn't do it! I don't know anything!
It wasn't me! I didn't do it!

95
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,310
Stop.

96
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,630
Yichuan and Xiaoqian's betrothal party
will be held tomorrow.

97
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:53,120
It's not auspicious to kill her now.

98
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:59,920
I'd suggest a lesser punishment for her.

99
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:02,310
Is that okay, darling?

100
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,600
I believe Xiaoqian will think so, too.

101
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,920
Nian is right.

102
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:14,750
Tomorrow is a big day for the Lu family.

103
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:19,070
Let's just ignore it today.

104
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,510
Darling.

105
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,870
Take some rest early.

106
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:30,390
You two will have to take care
of tomorrow's party.

107
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:01,840
It's all your fault!
Why are you so clumsy?

108
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:03,750
You almost caused me trouble!

109
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:22,420
♪How should I
embellish my life without you?♪

110
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:28,660
♪The thoughts of you
bring only the news about you♪

111
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:34,140
♪In front of the mirror,
stand half of me and half of you♪

112
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,740
♪In a trance,
it feels like we merged into one♪

113
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:43,380
♪The replay of the past scenes
goes on and on♪

114
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:47,580
♪Where else can I escape?♪

115
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:51,180
♪The satirical longing passes by♪

116
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:54,860
♪I struggle to break free from its grip♪

117
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:58,460
♪You even take away my happiness♪

118
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:02,060
♪Where else can I escape?♪

119
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:07,380
♪Memories occupy
the very last corner of my mind♪

120
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:10,580
♪Don't make me remember♪

121
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,580
♪Until this day♪

122
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:16,460
♪I was deeply loved by you♪
